 M. Anderson Graduate Award*(5)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><p>研究生手册：<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Nr20uKHLwolVBDh-tP_MLVz4GXN9pQJzze0mm5CgBFpWqo3qLFCIJKwzdxzAxBm-MmOdYF_ABCavfWZswDPHIO6-UhrItxd2F0CNhOvf4MKgz9SrOKnqLHAa_fVi" target="_blank">Graduate Handbook</a>(PDF)</p><p>教员列表：<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=OrMxo-DTLNk2B6kFvvvvvvZz9yf1ohR4sbsbtPgz8Mlz-Ii4dLf4NIHbYMnL8MnB-4yMptNx2s-oqbjcKt7uq-7WgUkoj" target="_blank">Faculty</a></p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=crr9MjJhk5gAridsllllllw71059d2IHW45q5q3tebV-J2V4pFFg4cJgTeVJIa4" target="_blank">Home</a> Department of Biochemistry, Virginia Tech</p><p>(2) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=9rpcSX3QkrW5UK1U_9U2Sw3KyhuPmvg3HGkr3r9-UHmR4l4LqUd6C3KJPzReHXMQ2hBYleBZIUtu_RdeU5fgy_3OrDnfgHPo1XEmK7__RPDD" target="_blank">How to Apply</a> Department of Biochemistry, Virginia Tech</p><p>(3) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=hrfXwivoLzABI5dOKKKKKKgJwDTtF5PfZ9yDyDSbVg6KtP6Ejp4kEpokt01U-uVGd9vSVQd0eGpUD1Q-dsDJt4C5guZMbIqEvB" target="_blank">Frequently Asked Questions</a> Department of Biochemistry, Virginia Tech</p><p>(4) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Nr20uKHswUvq6ocKeeeeeF5tN_aTA9lsn1kvy_HvC_PTng9En3xsXLasj-51c3XTjm51ymaL-38vTXRhbfMugeSX_FN5_aRzjdwG12SX_FB8CgbNK3ZdBafd34f-9BfX7YfCyVjCyc4dbAuzvnodfUopfUMObAeHLe" target="_blank">Biochemistry Graduate Catalog</a> Department of Biochemistry, Virginia Tech</p><p>(5) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ZrygfZipLBGgpjqnGGGGGGsb6WQZYV-fxtxt8UFblfWsVMLKqNOkqbLG_zWN6bYG_5YkOzWbV5FerbBTZ5mKZR6Og_WOTNodr_va2J6q" target="_blank">Financial Aid</a> Department of Biochemistry, Virginia Tech</p><h2>自然资源与环境科学学院</h2><p>弗吉尼亚理工自然资源与<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/环境科学" target="_blank">环境科学</a>学院（College of Natural Resources and Environment）开设有以下6个专业，分别是：</p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:33.98%">			<p><strong>专业名称</strong></p>			</td>			<td style="width