keting research）该项目不同于专业硕士学位（如<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/MBA" target="_blank">MBA</a>），竞争异常激烈，每年仅录取1-3名学生。面向以下两类申请者：	<ul>		<li>仅拥有学士学位，但想直接攻读PhD项目；</li>		<li>有明确的职业目标，计划在市场调研组织从事市场分析的岗位。*(2)</li>	</ul>	</li>	<li>PhD项目学制4年，要求申请者修读过微积分、<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/统计学" target="_blank">统计学</a>前置课程。所有学生必须做2年<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/助教" target="_blank">助教</a>和2年助研。市场营销系将提供<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/TA" target="_blank">TA</a>和<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/RA" target="_blank">RA</a><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/奖学金" target="_blank">奖学金</a>，涵盖4年学习期间所有费用。*(3)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=SrWl9Lu4kMv2wkv4gBsVnyPZqtkN8lUYC8HL_zGb_Wz2R1mG7R8uc5RLrHU8MQJTp0V3PncaCYd_mkQe_FuCX_upIYPzyc_CzGBQmx_UWMQJxk1Lmhi-XKoDK31mcauplf3MfEBuB2BPUaKPMGkfUpL0" target="_blank">Graduate Degrees</a> Marketing Department, Virginia Tech</p><p>(2) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=OrMxo-GDw-IwEQescccccgltcI0SLIk_1bjiSMmGTnp_skELzFW_PdC37UpI0Bz8HtRjLoYoYTx9P9MlgXZuXJy9TGosc_oEc3F7dYz2LTxmboaKADhU3NPa0_majSA_xer-HoDg4oAbkCB8xC5t" target="_blank">Masters Degree</a> Marketing Department, Virginia Tech</p><p>(3) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=rrcuJRvtkO9fNDoT222224jgxYcP8YEbOoiK3pgOU1eUZd7BclM4vw7AToZ_Z7lG6OWssLTLTI9CrkA_NHnOHqzygRPm2aP_SPGUeY6-d3GnPfyaiC4jioZaSKE1-yUGXFWcI8zLxt0TMAa" target="_blank">Doctoral Program</a> Marketing Department, Virginia Tech</p><p>(4) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=-rGz4OcCLXmqlADBfGpnNzw5RDi5nHG-O-uTm3Adt26oB45ujtRNSF3gd6h0jSilrOrrqnOFTfErS-0YfBI4XrOz7rxyblh0YSDldpJtM6oB45rEakJKKCU7cahpp2aCNoqQ4A_8g2FtZCqAFIPwrOk5KRsTqw-heKTpBIhxYpB2m_3tZ35mFo" target="_blank">Marketing Graduate Catalog</a> Virginia Tech</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>会计信息系统</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.1%">			<p>USNEWS排名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:13.42%">			<p>Unranked</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.1%">			<p>学费</p>			</t